                     <interp inst="t18480918-2086-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 1 sack, and 4 bushels of oats, chaff, and beans, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18480918-name-170" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-170" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-170" type="surname" value="PEACOCK"></interp>
