                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-173" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SMITH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, K</hi> 220). I was with the officer Parker, and saw what he has stated.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">ADAMS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
